<p>Mr. Muhlig is a member of the Caxton Club and the Society of American Archivists, and has completed advanced course work in appraisal theory at Northwestern University and the University of Texas at Austin. He also serves on the Advisory Council for the Harry Ransom Center at the University of Texas at Austin.</p>

